	<h2>API</h2>
	
You can access the system without any limitations using the following endpoint:
<code>http://www.serelex.org/MODEL/WORD</code>. The list of available models is presented below:

<ul>
<li><a href='http://www.serelex.org/find/en-patternsim-ukwac-wiki/ubuntu'>English PatternSim model</a>.</li>
<li><a href='http://www.serelex.org/find/fr-patternsim-frwac-wiki/belgique'>French PatternSim model</a>.</li>
<li><a href='http://www.serelex.org/find/ru-patternsim-ruwac-wiki/%D1%81%D0%BE%D0%BB%D1%8C'>Russian PatternSim model</a>.</li>
<li><a href='http://www.serelex.org/find/ru-skipgram-librusec/%D1%81%D0%BE%D0%BB%D1%8C'>Russian SkipGram model</a> also known as the <a href='http://russe.nlpub.ru/downloads/'>Russian Distributional Thesaurus</a>, RDT).</li>
<li><a href='http://www.serelex.org/find/pt-patternsim-wiki/lisboa'>Portugese PatternSim model</a>.</li>
</ul>

